<tbody>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle">
<ptxt>
U oba sustava detektiran je samo povijesni DTC
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle">
<ptxt>
Nakon što očistite DTC i izvršite test u vožnji, ponovno provjerite DTC. Ako je rezultat provjere u redu, onda je to povremena greška. 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
—
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle">
<ptxt>
&#34;Isključen upravljački modul sabirnice&#34; detektiran je u oba sustava (trenutni DTC)
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle">
<ptxt>
Izvršite &#34;Rješavanje problema isključene sabirnice komunikacije&#34; 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AHRAP70AA804004"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle">
<ptxt>
Samo &#34;Prekid komunikacije&#34; je detektiran u oba sustava (trenutni DTC)
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle">
<ptxt>
Izvršite &#34;Rješavanje problema prekida komunikacije&#34;
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AHRAP70AA804003"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" morerows = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle">
<ptxt>
Nema prikaza na SUZUKI alatu za skeniranje (nije moguće komunicirati sa svim sustavima).
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle">
<ptxt>
Provjerite je li moguće komunicirati sa SUZUKI alatom za skeniranje tako da ga spojite na drugo vozilo.
</ptxt>
</entry>
